social_posts.post_text: didn’t ask her to move home this time

heartbroken. no one prepares you for the phone call that will shatter your heart into a million pieces. my sweet alex, the one who made everyone smile, laugh until they can’t breath, and brought the party everywhere he went. the knot in my heart will never go away, a piece of me went to heaven, and i will never forget the love you brought to this earth in just 22 years. 

if life could give me one more minute, all i could think to say would be thank you, and hug you for all you’ve done to make everyone’s lives better. 

taken way too soon; paint the sky for us alex, watch over us everyday, i love you my angel , see you in heaven 🤍
